This repository contains various tools and scripts for operations of MC2
servers. Some tools are generic and can be used for various purposes.

Please refer to the MC2 operations manual for more information on most of
these: http://oss.wayfinder.com/wiki/operations_manual

wfconf/
A simple perl based configuration management tool including example
configurations and files for setting up MC2 servers

mc2conf/
Tool to simplify complex configurations of MC2, generates mc2control files.

wftee/
Tee with some extra features

monitoring/
tools related to monitoring of MC2, includes a generic Nagios
checker that uses Ganglia data

misc/
A couple of CGI binaries that presents MC2 configuration files as HTML 
